'''1917年新赫罗纳飓风'''（{{lang-en|1917 Nueva Gerona hurricane}}<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Christopher W. Landsea | author2 = David Glenn | author3 = William Bredemeyer | author4 = Michael Chenoweth | author5 = Ryan Ellis | author6 = John Gamache | author7 = Cary Mock | author8 = Ramon Perez | author9 = Ricardo Prieto | author10 = Jorge Sanchez-Sesma | author11 = Donna Thomas | author12 = Lenworth Woolcock | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2007-09-05 | accessdate = 2016-12-11 | title = A Reanalysis of the 1911–20 Atlantic Hurricane Database | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/reanal_1911-20.pdf | archivedate = 2016-05-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160514120307/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/reanal_1911-20.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>）是[[1995年大西洋飓风季|1995年]]的[[飓风欧帕尔|飓风欧帕尔]]以前吹袭[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[佛罗里达西北狭长地带|西北狭长地带]]的最强[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[1917年大西洋飓风季|1917年大西洋飓风季]]的第四个热带风暴和第二场飓风，最初是9月20日[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东海域出现的一场热带风暴。经过群岛后，气旋进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，于9月21日达到飓风强度，之后又成为二级飓风，于9月23日[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[牙买加|牙买加]]北岸。9月25日清晨，风暴达到四级飓风标准，并在不久后达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时240公里的最高强度。飓风当天从[[古巴|古巴]][[比那尔德里奥省|比那尔德里奥省]]东部登陆，此后不久就进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]并略有减弱。气旋回转北上，短暂对[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]构成威胁，但很快又转朝[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]前进。9月29日清晨，风暴以持续风速每小时185公里强度从佛罗里达州[[华尔顿堡滩_(佛罗里达州)|华尔顿堡滩]]附近登陆。进入陆地上空后，飓风急剧弱化，转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]后于9月30日逐渐消散。

小安的列斯群岛包括[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]、[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]和[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]在内的多个岛屿遭遇狂风暴雨。飓风对牙买加的[[芭蕉属|香蕉]]和椰树种植园构成重创，荷兰湾的通讯受到干扰，该岛北半部遭受的破坏最为严重，[[安东尼奥港|安东尼奥港]]有九人遇难。[[新赫罗纳|新赫罗纳]]许多建筑质量很好的建筑也被狂风摧毁，全城仅有十户民房留存。[[青年岛|青年岛]]一共受到价值约200万美元的损失，还有至少20人丧生。比那尔德里奥省部分果园和庄稼毁于一旦。路易斯安那州和[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]所受整体影响较小，基本局限于农作物和木材林受损，路易斯安那州有十人淹死。更东面的[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]有部分树木和房屋的屋顶受损，街道上散落着各种垃圾。佛罗里达州[[彭萨科拉_(佛罗里达州)|彭萨科拉]]的通讯中断，许多小船搁浅，多个码头、船坞及船库受到影响。彭萨科拉地区的损失总额估计为17万美元左右。佛罗里达州共有五人死亡，并且全部发生在[[克雷斯特韦_(佛罗里达州)|克雷斯特韦]]。飓风及其残留还在乔治亚州、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]产生降水。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|1917 Atlantic hurricane 4 track.png}}
[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月20日凌晨0点，[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东北偏东方向约260公里海域的开放[[低压槽|低压槽]]（可能是[[东风波|东风波]]）发展成热带风暴<ref name="hurdatmeta">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | deadurl = no | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | display-authors = etal | date = 2012-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | archivedate = 2015-09-30 }}</ref>。气旋向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]移动并稳步增强，于数小时后从[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]和[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]之间经过[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]。9月21日进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]后，风暴的强化速度加快，于当天达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准，次日又在经过[[海地|海地]]蒂布龙半岛（{{lang|en|Tiburon Peninsula}}）期间进一步增强成二级飓风。9月23日晚，气旋吹袭牙买加北岸，然后返回加勒比海。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月24日早上6点左右，风暴在朝西北移动期间达到三级飓风强度并袭击[[开曼布拉克|开曼布拉克]]。9月25日清晨，气旋成为四级飓风。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>

古巴气象研究所的拉蒙·佩雷斯（{{lang|pt|Ramón Perez}}）估计，飓风气压于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月25日中午12点降至928毫巴（百帕，27.4英寸汞柱）的最低值。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的研究人员据此推断风暴的最高[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]为240公里。<ref name="hurdatmeta" />达到最高强度后不久，风暴掠过[[青年岛|青年岛]]。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月25日下午18点，气旋以最高强度从[[古巴|古巴]][[比那尔德里奥省|比那尔德里奥省]]东部[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，并在当晚进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]。9月27日清晨，飓风强度回落至三级标准。风暴一度总体朝北面的路易斯安那州东南部逼近，但很快又于次日转向东北。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月29日凌晨2点，气旋以持续风速每小时185公里强度从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[华尔顿堡滩_(佛罗里达州)|华尔顿堡滩]]附近登陆。进入陆地上空后，飓风急剧减弱，不到12小时就消退成热带风暴，再于9月30日清晨在乔治亚州上空同[[锋_(气象)|锋区]]逐渐融合并转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，风暴残留在约六小时后消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

飓风的最低气压为928毫巴（百帕，27.42英寸汞柱），是历史上登陆古巴时强度第三高的风暴，仅次于921毫巴（百帕，27.23英寸汞柱）的[[1924年古巴飓风|1924年古巴飓风]]和915毫巴（百帕，27.02英寸汞柱）的[[1932年古巴飓风|1932年古巴飓风]]<ref name="Partagas">{{cite report | author = Jose F. Partagas | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | year = 1993 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/impacthurrhist.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040631/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/impacthurrhist.pdf | deadurl = no | title = Impact on Hurricane History of a Revised Lowest Pressure at Havana (Cuba) During the October 11, 1846 Hurricane | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>。气旋登陆佛罗里达西北狭长地带时气压低至949毫巴（百帕，28.02英寸汞柱），追平1882年一场飓风所创纪录，直到1995年才被飓风欧帕尔以945毫巴（百帕，27.82英寸汞柱）打破<ref name="u.s. hurricanes">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | title = Chronological List of All Hurricanes: 1851 – 2012 | date = 2013 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161113005842/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-11-13 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==

=== 加勒比地区 ===
9月21日，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]向[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]发布公告，提醒有[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]存在<ref name="MWR">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1917.pdf | title = Section III. – Forecasts | author = Henry C. Frankenfield | date = 1917-10-01 | work = [[美国国家气象局|Weather Bureau]] | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | location = [[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|Washington, D.C.]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235535/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1917.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

飓风在东加勒比群岛产生狂风暴雨<ref name="hurdatmeta" />，牙买加的[[芭蕉属|香蕉]]和椰树种植园遭受重创，荷兰湾（{{lang|en|Holland Bay}}）的通讯受到干扰<ref name="DailyGleaner">{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Gleaner | year = 1917 | title = Storm News Received From the Various Districts}}</ref>，该岛北半部受到的破坏最为严重<ref name="MWR" />。[[安东尼奥港|安东尼奥港]]的海关被毁，还有一所酒店严重受损，市内九人丧生<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240816/the_pantagraph/ | title = Hurricane Kills Nine | date = 1917-09-25 | newspaper = The Pantagraph | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | location = Kingston, Jamaica | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190609175528/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240816/the_pantagraph/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。古巴[[新赫罗纳|新赫罗纳]]许多建筑质量很好的建筑也被狂风摧毁，全城变得满目疮痍<ref name="MWR" />，仅有十幢民宅依然屹立<ref name="nyt">{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5236270/the_new_york_times/ | title = Hurricane Damage Isles of Pines | date = 1919-09-29 | newspaper = The New York Times | page = 3 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | location = Havana, Cuba | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610130259/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5236270/the_new_york_times/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。某大型种植园内除房屋以外所有的建筑都被摧毁，园内所有的鸡都在风暴中死亡<ref name="df">{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5241076/the_kingston_daily_freeman/ | title = Brinnier's Place Wrecked by Storm | date = 1917-10-05 | newspaper = Daily Freeman | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190616055137/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5241076/the_kingston_daily_freeman/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。[[青年岛|青年岛]]各地的损失总额约为200万美元，岛上粮食储备毁于一旦<ref name="nyt" />。海上有多艘船只沉没或失踪，导致“多人”丧生<ref>{{cite news | location = Havana, Cuba | date = 1917-09-29 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240932/the_topeka_daily_capital/ | title = Hurricane Sweeps Isles of Pines | newspaper = The Topeka Capital-Journal | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190605222753/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240932/the_topeka_daily_capital/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。全岛至少有20人遇难<ref name="lpr">{{cite news | location = Havana, Cuba | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5241004/la_plata_republican/ | title = Tropical Storm on Southern Coast | date = 1917-10-05 | publisher = La Plata Republican | page = 3 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | archive-date = 2019-06-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190611164039/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5241004/la_plata_republican/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>，另有报导声称死亡人数高达数百<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240980/the_salina_evening_journal/ | title = Gale Hits Isle Pines | date = 1917-10-06 | newspaper = The Salina Evening Journal | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610023600/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5240980/the_salina_evening_journal/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。比那尔德里奥省部分果园和庄稼被毁<ref name="MWR" />。救灾机构向当时的[[古巴总统|古巴总统]][[马里奥·加西亚·梅诺卡尔|马里奥·加西亚·梅诺卡尔]]（{{lang|en|Mario García Menocal}}）和美国请求援助<ref name="nyt" />。伯恩赛德酒店的厨房向风暴灾民提供食品<ref name="df" />。

=== 美国 ===
[[File:1917hurricanerainfallmap.png|thumb]]

9月23日，[[西棕榈滩|西棕榈滩]]至[[博卡格兰德_(佛罗里达州)|博卡格兰德]]（{{lang|en|Boca Grande}}）之间的佛罗里达州沿海地区收到[[热带气旋警告|东北风暴警告]]<ref name="MWR" />。9月25日，气象局发布公告，称风暴强度不明，建议墨西哥湾的海上交通维持警戒状态<ref name="OgdenStandard">{{cite news | newspaper = The Ogden Standard | year = 1917 | title = Storm Sweeps Over Jamaica}}</ref>。9月25日，佛罗里达州[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]至[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]还接获飓风警告。9月26日，[[密西西比州|密西西比州]][[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]至[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]同样收到警告。由于气象部门难以确定气旋动向，警告一度中止，但很快又在风暴开始回转东北后再度生效。9月27至28日，新奥尔良的船只出行取消。飓风从该市东侧经过后，海上交通恢复正常。气旋的移动速度缓慢，因此吹袭美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区的时间晚于预期。<ref name="MWR" />

风暴的[[雨带|雨带]]在[[普拉克明堂区_(路易斯安那州)|普拉克明堂区]]的[[布尔伍德_(路易斯安那州)|布尔伍德]]（{{lang|en|Burrwood}}）降下160毫米雨量<ref name="MWR" />。由于[[凯瑟琳湖|凯瑟琳湖]]（{{lang|en|Lake Catherine}}）附近的铁轨受到[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]，[[路易斯维尔与纳什维尔铁路|路易斯维尔与纳什维尔铁路]]（{{lang|en|Louisville and Nashville Railroad}}）变更列车的出行线路。飓风还令路易斯安那州和密西西比州的农作物和木材林受损。<ref name="Galveston">{{cite news | newspaper = The Galveston Daily News | year = 1917 | title = Reports Indicate Slight Life Loss}}</ref>路易斯安那州普拉克明堂区的[[布拉斯_(路易斯安那州)|布拉斯]]（{{lang|en|Buras}}）有多幢建筑在[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]冲击下出现位移，从地基上脱落<ref name="MWR" />，当地还有一名八岁男童因气旋丧生<ref name="hurdatmeta" />。“旺纳号”（{{lang|en|Wanna}}）渔船在[[霍玛_(路易斯安那州)|霍玛]]附近沉没，又导致九人遇难<ref name="tdfp">{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5299694/the_daily_free_press/ | title = Pensacola Gets Cut Off by Gale; 3 States in Path Hurricane | date = 1917-09-29 | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = The Daily Free Press | pages = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190609175531/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5299694/the_daily_free_press/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。[[比洛克西_(密西西比州)|比洛克西]]由于警告及时，捕虾船没有遭受严重损伤<ref name="Galveston" />。[[格尔夫波特_(密西西比州)|格尔夫波特]]部分街道暂时禁止汽车及其他交通工具通行<ref name="tes">{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5299814/the_evening_star/ | title = Gulf States Hit by Hurricane | date = 1917-09-29 | newspaper = The Evening Star | page = 2 | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610080701/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5299814/the_evening_star/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。

阿拉巴马州的[[蒙哥马利_(阿拉巴马州)|蒙哥马利]]降雨量超过125毫米<ref name="Galveston" />，[[阿拉巴马河|阿拉巴马河]]（{{lang|en|Alabama River}}）下游流域因此收到洪水公告<ref name="MWR" />。[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]的[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]训练基地谢里登营（{{lang|en|Camp Sheridan}}）内多条街道被淹，积水至少有数英寸深<ref name="tdfp" />。[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]有部分树木倒塌，电话和电报线路受损，导致通讯中断<ref name="Galveston" /><ref name="tes" />。部分房屋失去屋顶，阳台被狂风刮落。警方切断供电，并拦下街上的车辆。<ref name="tes" />当地没有船只失踪，码头的损伤程度基本可以忽略不计<ref name="Galveston" />。

佛罗里达州[[彭萨科拉_(佛罗里达州)|彭萨科拉]]的通讯中断，但经事后确定，城内的无线电发射塔并未被毁<ref name="Galveston" />。包括“昆西号”（{{lang|en|USS Quincy}}）在内的多艘小型船只搁浅，多个码头、船坞及船库受损<ref name="MWR" />。彭萨科拉地区的损失总额估计为17万美元左右<ref name="MWR" />。路易斯维尔与纳什维尔铁路位于该市附近部分路段被2.4米的洪水淹没，还有多座铁路桥梁被冲毁<ref name="tdfp" />。[[瓦尔帕莱索_(佛罗里达州)|瓦尔帕莱索]]的风暴潮有2.3米高<ref name="barnes">{{cite book | author = Jay Barnes | title = Florida's Hurricane History | publisher = University of North Carolina Press | date = 2007 | page = 99 | isbn = 978-0-8078-3068-0 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dMx5bkZKxioC&printsec=frontcover&dq=florida%27s+hurricane+history&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dmZSVYb6N8G8sQWh04GIBQ&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=florida's%20hurricane%20history&f=false | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | archive-date = 2020-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201222082731/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dMx5bkZKxioC&printsec=frontcover&dq=florida%27s+hurricane+history&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dmZSVYb6N8G8sQWh04GIBQ&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=florida's%20hurricane%20history&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[奥卡鲁沙县|奥卡鲁沙县]]和[[圣罗萨县_(佛罗里达州)|圣罗萨县]]的木材林受到显著破坏，庄稼、建筑和牲畜也受到影响<ref name="MWR" />。佛罗里达州西北沿海地区狂风肆虐，[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]测得70公里的阵风时速<ref name="MWR" />。[[克雷斯特韦_(佛罗里达州)|克雷斯特韦]]共有五人遇难<ref name="MWR" />。除此以外，风暴及其残留还在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]产生降水<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065316/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | title = Report No. 3 Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes | author = R. W. Schoner | author2 = S. Molansky | date = 1956-07 | work = United States Hydrographic Office | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-12 | location = Washington, D.C. | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

